  "description": "The image depicts three Allium flower stalks rising from a dark background. The flowers are in varying stages of bloom, with the most prominent one being fully open and displaying numerous tiny, star-shaped purple florets. The stalks are slender and green, providing a strong vertical emphasis. A delicate spiderweb stretches between two of the stalks, adding a subtle textural element to the composition. The lighting is soft and highlights the texture of the flowers and the delicate web.",
